---
title: Rosemary Demi-Glace Chicken with Roasted Carrots & Parsnips
description: These, friends, are not your average pork chops. In fact, our chefs gave ‘em a steak-like treatment, transforming the everyday protein into something above and beyond. The chops are seared to perfection, then drizzled with an ultra-savory, rosemary-flecked pan sauce. The sides? Just as impressive. We’re serving up creamy mashed potatoes and roasted carrots and onion wedges to round everything out. Prepare for a flavor explosion.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/624d937d528b4a246203f8b8-54642970.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/rosemary-demi-glace-chicken-624d937d528b4a246203f8b8-7bf918d8.pdf
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 510 kcal
  fat: 21 g
  saturated fat: 7 g
  carbohydrates: 45 g
  sugar: 18 g
  protein: 35 g
  fiber: 11 g
  sodium: 560 mg
